    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may add the following traits to your forms:</p>\n<p><strong>Powerful Charge:</strong> Choose one natural attack the target possesses. When charging, that attack deals damage as if it were one size larger and receives 1-1/2 times the target&#8217;s Strength bonus to damage instead of 1 times.</p>\n<p><strong>Push/Pull:</strong> Choose one natural attack the target possesses. On a successful attack against a creature of equal or smaller size, the target may attempt a bull rush, drag, or reposition check as a free action that does not provoke an attack of opportunity.</p>\n",
